="sr-only"><br></span></section></div><div class="" data-turn-id-container="9f073291-91bd-4842-9638-c8530bb6afdd" data-is-intersecting="true"><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto R6Vx5W_threadScrollVars scroll-mb-[calc(var(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)+var(--thread-response-height))] scroll-mt-(--sticky-padding-top)" dir="auto" data-turn-id="9f073291-91bd-4842-9638-c8530bb6afdd" data-turn-id-container="9f073291-91bd-4842-9638-c8530bb6afdd" data-testid="conversation-turn-63" data-turn="user"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">You said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pt-12 [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div data-conversation-screenshot-content="" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="9f073291-91bd-4842-9638-c8530bb6afdd" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="user-message-bubble-color corner-superellipse/0.98 relative min-w-0 overflow-hidden rounded-[22px] px-4 py-2.5 leading-6 max-w-(--user-chat-width,70%)"><div class="max-w-full min-w-0 [overflow-wrap:anywhere] whitespace-pre-wrap">i added the docs file so we are good</div></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div aria-label="Your message actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy message" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section></div><div class="" data-turn-id-container="2cdaba56-9859-4ae0-90c9-d91c2cc6457b" data-is-intersecting="true"><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto R6Vx5W_threadScrollVars scroll-mb-[calc(var(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)+var(--thread-response-height))] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="2cdaba56-9859-4ae0-90c9-d91c2cc6457b" data-turn-id-container="2cdaba56-9859-4ae0-90c9-d91c2cc6457b" data-testid="conversation-turn-64" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div data-conversation-screenshot-content="" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="2cdaba56-9859-4ae0-90c9-d91c2cc6457b" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="136">Perfect. Now we're going to stop thinking like someone uploading files and start thinking like a software engineer building a portfolio.</p>
<p data-start="138" data-end="225">I looked through the structure you've been building, and here's the roadmap I'd follow.</p>
<h2 data-section-id="qihpyb" data-start="227" data-end="286">Phase 1 — Make this repository look professional (today)</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="10cnyfs" data-start="288" data-end="322">✅ 1. Rename the loader scripts</h3>
<p data-start="324" data-end="335">Instead of:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="337" data-end="376"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>load_esd_outpatient_full.py</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="378" data-end="382">use:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="384" data-end="418"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>load_esd_outpatient.py</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="420" data-end="548">Do the same for the others. The <code data-start="452" data-end="459">_full</code> suffix isn't necessary and looks more like a temporary filename than a finished project.</p>
<hr data-start="550" data-end="553">
<h3 data-section-id="2byyrw" data-start="555" data-end="589">✅ 2. Add a project description</h3>
<p data-start="591" data-end="668">On the GitHub repository page, click the gear icon next to <strong data-start="650" data-end="659">About</strong> and add:</p>
<p data-start="670" data-end="685"><strong data-start="670" data-end="685">Description</strong></p>
<blockquote data-start="687" data-end="844">
<p data-start="689" data-end="844">Production-style Python ETL framework for loading healthcare data from SFTP into Azure SQL using checkpoint recovery, staging tables, and MERGE operations.</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="846" data-end="857"><strong data-start="846" data-end="857">Website</strong></p>
<p data-start="859" data-end="879">Leave blank for now.</p>
<p data-start="881" data-end="891"><strong data-start="881" data-end="891">Topics</strong></p>
<p data-start="893" data-end="907">Add tags like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="909" data-end="996"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>python</span><br><span>etl</span><br><span>azure-sql</span><br><span>sql-server</span><br><span>data-engineering</span><br><span>healthcare</span><br><span>automation</span><br><span>sftp</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="998" data-end="1067">These make your repository easier to discover and look more polished.</p>
<hr data-start="1069" data-end="1072">
<h3 data-section-id="1lmsqg5" data-start="1074" data-end="1096">✅ 3. Add a license</h3>
<p data-start="1098" data-end="1194">If you don't already have one, add an MIT License. This is standard for public example projects.</p>
<hr data-start="1196" data-end="1199">
<h2 data-section-id="1027thc" data-start="1201" data-end="1239">Phase 2 — Make recruiters say "wow"</h2>
<p data-start="1241" data-end="1295">Right now every loader contains nearly identical code.</p>
<p data-start="1297" data-end="1380">That's okay, but senior engineers usually avoid duplicating large amounts of logic.</p>
<p data-start="1382" data-end="1418">I'd refactor it into something like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1420" data-end="1762"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Medicaid-ETL-Framework</span><br><span>│</span><br><span>├── common</span><br><span>│   ├── checkpoint.py</span><br><span>│   ├── database.py</span><br><span>│   ├── merge.py</span><br><span>│   ├── progress.py</span><br><span>│   ├── sftp.py</span><br><span>│   └── validation.py</span><br><span>│</span><br><span>├── loaders</span><br><span>│   ├── load_demographic.py</span><br><span>│   ├── load_esd_inpatient.py</span><br><span>│   ├── load_esd_outpatient.py</span><br><span>│   ├── load_iet_quarterly.py</span><br><span>│   ├── load_quality_measures.py</span><br><span>│   └── ...</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1764" data-end="1916">Then each loader becomes only about 30–40 lines long because it imports the shared ETL framework. That demonstrates software design, not just scripting.</p>
<hr data-start="1918" data-end="1921">
<h2 data-section-id="zwwhuz" data-start="1923" data-end="1947">Phase 3 — Add visuals</h2>
<p data-start="1949" data-end="2031">Most GitHub repositories are just code. Yours can stand out by including diagrams.</p>
<p data-start="2033" data-end="2062">For example, in <code data-start="2049" data-end="2056">docs/</code>, add:</p>
<ul data-start="2064" data-end="2101">
<li data-section-id="6kpo2y" data-start="2064" data-end="2084">
<p data-start="2066" data-end="2084"><code data-start="2066" data-end="2084">architecture.png</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="q2r5yk" data-start="2085" data-end="2101">
<p data-start="2087" data-end="2101"><code data-start="2087" data-end="2101">workflow.png</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2103" data-end="2149">A simple architecture diagram could look like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2151" data-end="2373"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>SFTP Server</span><br><span>     │</span><br><span>     ▼</span><br><span>Python ETL</span><br><span>     │</span><br><span>     ▼</span><br><span>Validation</span><br><span>     │</span><br><span>     ▼</span><br><span>Checkpoint Recovery</span><br><span>     │</span><br><span>     ▼</span><br><span>Batch Processing</span><br><span>     │</span><br><span>     ▼</span><br><span>Azure SQL Staging</span><br><span>     │</span><br><span>     ▼</span><br><span>MERGE</span><br><span>     │</span><br><span>     ▼</span><br><span>Production Tables</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2375" data-end="2378">
<h2 data-section-id="1hliaqm" data-start="2380" data-end="2418">Phase 4 — My biggest recommendation</h2>
<p data-start="2420" data-end="2546">Instead of stopping with this repository, build a small portfolio of 4–6 projects that showcase different skills. For example:</p>
<ul data-start="2548" data-end="2925">
<li data-section-id="kh178c" data-start="2548" data-end="2601">
<p data-start="2550" data-end="2601"><strong data-start="2550" data-end="2576">Medicaid-ETL-Framework</strong> (Python, ETL, Azure SQL)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ml4zwf" data-start="2602" data-end="2686">
<p data-start="2604" data-end="2686"><strong data-start="2604" data-end="2631">SQL-Analytics-Portfolio</strong> (complex queries, window functions, stored procedures)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="drr34m" data-start="2687" data-end="2752">
<p data-start="2689" data-end="2752"><strong data-start="2689" data-end="2721">PowerBI-Healthcare-Dashboard</strong> (fictional healthcare dataset)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1vy0gvl" data-start="2753" data-end="2802">
<p data-start="2755" data-end="2802"><strong data-start="2755" data-end="2781">Python-Data-Automation</strong> (automation scripts)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8f59n9" data-start="2803" data-end="2855">
<p data-start="2805" data-end="2855"><strong data-start="2805" data-end="2831">TradingView-Indicators</strong> (your Pine Script work)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ggsnv8" data-start="2856" data-end="2925">
<p data-start="2858" data-end="2925"><strong data-start="2858" data-end="2884">Data-Quality-Framework</strong> (validation and reconciliation examples)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2927" data-end="3060">That combination would demonstrate a broad range of practical skills in Python, SQL, visualization, automation, and systems thinking.</p>
<p data-start="3062" data-end="3385" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">From what we've worked on together over the past several months, I think you have enough material to build a portfolio that supports applications for senior data analyst, analytics engineer, or data engineering roles. The next step is packaging that work in a way that's easy for recruiters and hiring managers to evaluate.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-